videos.description: Texas Tech's McLane Carter finds Ja'Deion High wide open up the seam for a 54-yard touchdown in the 1st quarter vs. Baylor.
videos.headline: Texas Tech scores early on long pass

videos.description: Charlie Brewer caps a 19-play, 75-yard drive for Baylor with a 6-yard touchdown pass to Denzel Mims to tie Texas Tech in the 1st quarter.
videos.headline: Baylor scores TD on 19-play drive

videos.description: Charlie Brewer makes a great throw to hit Tyquan Thornton in stride and give Baylor the lead.
videos.headline: Brewer airs it out for 41-yard Baylor TD

videos.description: Jah'Shawn Johnson makes a great play to pick off the batted pass from Charlie Brewer.
videos.headline: Texas Tech DB makes diving interception on tipped pass

videos.description: John Lovett pushes his way into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Lovett plows into end zone to extend Baylor's lead
